      • changeViewCB

        public abstract ActionCallback changeViewCB(java.lang.String viewId,
                                            java.lang.String subId)
        Changes currently selected view and subview (if any).

        When default subview is requested:
        - if the view had never been selected then the first subview is selected
        - otherwise subview won't be changed

        It's an error when a view has no subviews and subId is not null.

        Parameters:
        viewId - id of view to be selected
        subId - id of subview to be selected
        Returns:
        callback which will be set to done if new content was selected or to rejected if content didn't change.
